---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';import matrix from '../../../proof/shootout/architectures/matrix.json';
const candidates=matrix.dimensions.candidates;
---
<Layout title="Output architecture shootout"><header><p class="eyebrow">Compiler Shootout v1 · Axis B</p><h1>Output architecture: no winner</h1><p>The exact 32-cell matrix remains critically incomplete. The documented weight profile is not applied and no score is calculated.</p></header><section><h2>Separate Axis B verdict</h2><div class="counts"><b>87 passed</b><b>5 failed</b><b>212 blocked</b><b>80 not-run</b></div><p><strong>Weights applied?</strong> no · <strong>Winner?</strong> no</p><p>Architecture weight profile: API/DOM/behavior/client/SSR/hydration/node preservation/package/types/exports/styles/consumer gates are mandatory; hard failures or incomplete critical cells disqualify weighting. There is deliberately no combined Axis A + Axis B score.</p></section><section><h2>Candidate table</h2><div class="table" tabindex="0" role="region" aria-label="Architecture candidates; scroll horizontally on smaller screens"><table><thead><tr><th scope="col">Candidate</th><th scope="col">Cells</th><th scope="col">Verdict</th></tr></thead><tbody>{candidates.map(c=><tr><th scope="row">{c}</th><td>8</td><td>incomplete; not weighted</td></tr>)}</tbody></table></div><p>Consumer evidence is reported separately: <strong>10 passed / 0 failed / 21 blocked / 6 not-run</strong>.</p><p class="caveat">Evidence modes include mapped, prepared, and executed. Mapped/prepared source evidence is not executed parity; missing measurements remain missing. The immutable 164/164 control authority is separate and unchanged.</p><p><a href="/receipts/shootout-architecture.json">Drill down to all 32 cell receipts →</a> · <a href="/receipts/shootout-consumers.json">Consumer receipts →</a></p></section></Layout>
<style>header,section{max-width:900px;margin:35px auto}.eyebrow{color:#64748b;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700}h1{font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,45px);line-height:1.1}p{line-height:1.6}.counts{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:10px}.counts b,.caveat{padding:16px;background:#f1f5f9;border-radius:8px}.table{display:block;width:100%;max-width:100%;overflow-x:auto;border:1px solid #d8dde5;border-radius:8px;background:#fff}table{width:100%;min-width:520px;border-collapse:collapse}th,td{text-align:left;padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd}@media(max-width:700px){header,section{margin:24px auto}.counts{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}@media(max-width:420px){.counts{grid-template-columns:1fr}}</style>
